---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout title="Changes in Astra UI">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-16 py-12">
    <header class="space-y-4">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-neutral-900">Changes</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">Stay up to date with the latest improvements and features in Astra UI.</p>
    </header>

    <section class="space-y-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-neutral-900">Latest Updates</h2>

      <div class="space-y-12">
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-neutral-900">Version 0.4.5</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-neutral-600">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="mr-2">•</span>
              <span>Added JavaScript and TypeScript plugins for enhanced code editing capabilities</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="mr-2">•</span>
              <span>Improved dark mode borders and adjusted spacing and roundedness for better visual consistency</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="mr-2">•</span>
              <span>Fixed issues with table view updates to improve performance and reduce unnecessary calls</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <hr class="border-t border-neutral-200" />

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-neutral-900">Version 0.4.0</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-neutral-600">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="mr-2">•</span>
              <span>Implemented horizontal virtualized scrolling for improved performance with large datasets</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="mr-2">•</span>
              <span>Added new features: insert timestamp, UUID, null, and undefined values in cells</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="mr-2">•</span>
              <span>Fixed keyboard navigation issues in menus and improved overall accessibility</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <hr class="border-t border-neutral-200" />

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-neutral-900">Version 0.3.0</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-neutral-600">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="mr-2">•</span>
              <span>Redesigned prompt plugin for improved user experience</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="mr-2">•</span>
              <span>Added editor statement highlight plugin for improved code readability</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="mr-2">•</span>
              <span>Fixed various editor-related bugs and improved stability</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-neutral-900">What's Next?</h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
        We're constantly working on improving Astra UI. Stay tuned for more exciting features and enhancements in upcoming releases!
      </p>
      <a
        href="https://outerbase.com/docs/astra-ui/roadmap"
        class="inline-block bg-blue-500 text-white font-semibold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-600 transition-colors"
      >
        View Roadmap
      </a>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
